dc_description_s: Cover title. Mounted in folding cover with cloth spine. Copper plate, hand colored. Relief shown by hachures. Includes introductory text with charts and insets of Tokyo, Kyoto, Osaka, Peking, Shanghai, and Canton. Mercator projection. 1 map: col.; 90 x 135 cm. folded to 19 x 13 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
